title: Let's Learn Japanese - A Video Course
description:
A Full Television Course 
Let&#039;s Learn Japanese is for those who wish to learn the fundamentals of the Japanese language. Each leaaon is thirty minutes long and is based on the material from the series Yan and the Japanese People. The use of video materials featuring the experiences of a young foreign man who has just arrived in Tokyo, makes the tasl of language learning more enjoyable and ensures also that viewers will pick up a great deal of information about contemporary Japanese life.
